reviews.text:
Compact little mall that serves it purpose.
We visited Hong Kong last year and stayed in Laguna City for 3 weeks.
We did our shopping here, ate at their local restaurants (even at their McDonald's), and simply hanged around.  It may not have the fanfare of one of those fancy shopping malls that HK is famous for but I felt like at home reminding me from my local malls in Kanata Ont. Canada.  It can be a bit puzzling t navigate it but cozy.  Will come here again this summer.
where to let me hv unforgettable exp.
Good residential area.
Hv all the basic
